2	Ahmedabad	uhi	2026-03-22 08:08:01.476404	\N	llama-3.3-70b-versatile	You are an environmental analyst on the AETRIX pan-India platform. Summarize this Urban Heat Island analysis for Ahmedabad in 3 bullet points for a municipal officer. City mean LST: 26.1°C. Anomalous locations: 12 out of 142. Top hotspot: East Ahmedabad Commercial Zone at 28.3°C (Low). Be concise. Use plain language. Flag the most urgent area.	As an environmental analyst, I've summarized the Urban Heat Island analysis for Ahmedabad in 3 key points for you:\n\n* The city's average temperature is 26.1°C, which is a relatively moderate temperature.\n* There are 12 locations in the city that are significantly hotter than the rest, with the East Ahmedabad Commercial Zone being the hottest at 28.3°C.\n* **I urge immediate attention to the East Ahmedabad Commercial Zone**, as it has been identified as the top hotspot, and its high temperature can have adverse effects on the health and comfort of people living and working there.
